[
    {
        "text": "“Hi.",
        "start": 0.591,
        "duration": 0.499
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m Peter Hedges, writer and\ndirector of “Ben Is Back.”",
        "start": 1.09,
        "duration": 4.14
    },
    {
        "text": "Ben Burns, played\nby Lucas Hedges,",
        "start": 5.23,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "comes home unexpectedly\non Christmas Eve Day.",
        "start": 7.45,
        "duration": 3.87
    },
    {
        "text": "And he’s with\nhis mother Holly,",
        "start": 11.32,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "played by Julia Roberts.",
        "start": 13.42,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "She’s taken him\nChristmas shopping",
        "start": 15.43,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "so he’ll have appropriate\nclothes to wear",
        "start": 16.87,
        "duration": 2.07
    },
    {
        "text": "at church that night.",
        "start": 18.94,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "They’ve just come from\na 12-step meeting.",
        "start": 20.32,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "Ben is in recovery\nfrom heroin addiction.”",
        "start": 23.2,
        "duration": 5.305
    },
    {
        "text": "“Looks like she’s gonna have\nyou try on the whole store.”",
        "start": 28.505,
        "duration": 3.529
    },
    {
        "text": "“I love what both actors\nare bringing to this scene.",
        "start": 32.034,
        "duration": 3.586
    },
    {
        "text": "They start in very\ndifferent places",
        "start": 35.62,
        "duration": 4.26
    },
    {
        "text": "from where they end up.",
        "start": 39.88,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "Lucas as Ben has\nthis rich inner life",
        "start": 41.83,
        "duration": 2.29
    },
    {
        "text": "at the beginning of the scene.",
        "start": 44.12,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "There’s this\ndangerous something",
        "start": 45.37,
        "duration": 2.185
    },
    {
        "text": "coursing through him.",
        "start": 47.555,
        "duration": 0.875
    },
    {
        "text": "He has a secret.”",
        "start": 48.43,
        "duration": 0.708
    },
    {
        "text": "“Pockets.”",
        "start": 52.174,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "“This is humiliating.”",
        "start": 61.433,
        "duration": 2.669
    },
    {
        "text": "“No, this is love.”",
        "start": 64.102,
        "duration": 3.703
    },
    {
        "text": "“Holly’s oblivious.”",
        "start": 67.805,
        "duration": 1.462
    },
    {
        "text": "“Free to go.”",
        "start": 69.267,
        "duration": 0.583
    },
    {
        "text": "“You didn’t check my shoes.”",
        "start": 72.978,
        "duration": 3.492
    },
    {
        "text": "“Then Holly becomes concerned.",
        "start": 76.47,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "And Julia’s switch from\nhappy mother shopping",
        "start": 78.39,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "with her son to concerned\nand panicked mother is — “",
        "start": 82.47,
        "duration": 4.485
    },
    {
        "text": "“Mom, it was a joke.”",
        "start": 86.955,
        "duration": 0.975
    },
    {
        "text": "“ — so powerful.”",
        "start": 87.93,
        "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
        "text": "“Excuse me — can I get a\nkey to this door, please?”",
        "start": 89.19,
        "duration": 2.745
    },
    {
        "text": "“This scene is a\nmicrocosm for the film —",
        "start": 91.935,
        "duration": 3.345
    },
    {
        "text": "that in Holly,\nat the beginning,",
        "start": 95.28,
        "duration": 1.98
    },
    {
        "text": "you see the hope\nshe has that this",
        "start": 97.26,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "is going to be a fun thing.",
        "start": 99.72,
        "duration": 1.212
    },
    {
        "text": "She’s going to get\nclothes for him.",
        "start": 100.932,
        "duration": 1.458
    },
    {
        "text": "And Ben has a secret.",
        "start": 102.39,
        "duration": 1.23
    },
    {
        "text": "Ben has something\nhe’s not saying.",
        "start": 103.62,
        "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
        "text": "And then she checks him\nbecause she has concerns.",
        "start": 106.7,
        "duration": 4.45
    },
    {
        "text": "She’s always worried.",
        "start": 111.15,
        "duration": 1.15
    },
    {
        "text": "But she’s not paying\nfull attention.",
        "start": 112.3,
        "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
        "text": "But she think she is.",
        "start": 114.42,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "And she thinks she’s\ncovered all the tracks.",
        "start": 116.31,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "And then he reminds her, no,\nshe didn’t check everything.",
        "start": 118.65,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "And then watching how\nshe can, on a dime,",
        "start": 122.49,
        "duration": 4.47
    },
    {
        "text": "flip from the happy\nmom to panicked",
        "start": 126.96,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "mom and fierce mom — “",
        "start": 129.69,
        "duration": 3.261
    },
    {
        "text": "“Where did you get this?",
        "start": 132.951,
        "duration": 1.419
    },
    {
        "text": "I’ve been with you\nthe whole time.”",
        "start": 134.37,
        "duration": 1.855
    },
    {
        "text": "“Excuse me!”",
        "start": 136.225,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "“The girl at the meeting.”",
        "start": 136.725,
        "duration": 1.083
    },
    {
        "text": "“And Ben going from cocky\nand confident to reduced",
        "start": 137.808,
        "duration": 5.232
    },
    {
        "text": "and regressing in age and\nfearful and apologetic — “",
        "start": 143.04,
        "duration": 8.836
    },
    {
        "text": "“You think I’m an idiot.”",
        "start": 151.876,
        "duration": 2.204
    },
    {
        "text": "“All right.",
        "start": 154.08,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Can you please just\nexit the store?”",
        "start": 154.58,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "“Yes.”",
        "start": 156.08,
        "duration": 0.85
    },
    {
        "text": "“The range where they both\ngo in the scene, the number",
        "start": 156.93,
        "duration": 3.15
    },
    {
        "text": "of places they go, is\nemblematic of all the places",
        "start": 160.08,
        "duration": 4.89
    },
    {
        "text": "we go in the film.”",
        "start": 164.97,
        "duration": 2.09
    }
]